ckup errors are still generic\\.\\\\n'\n\\)\nif entry not in text:\n    if marker in text:\n        text = text\\.replace\\(marker, marker \\+ entry, 1\\)\n    else:\n        text \\+= '\\\\n' \\+ entry\n    history_path\\.write_text\\(text, encoding='utf-8'\\)\nPY$/": {
